DiNapoli AlertHpst On April nd when everyone was calling for lower lows we predicted Dow support at the area Days later the market had rallied from there an incredible points Also our DoubleRePo pattern called the market top in January before the recent bear market This is when Joe suggested traders move to cash etc It was a truly classic DiNapoli pattern with excellent advice from Joe too You can learn how these market calls were calculated on the following web pages archives This information is available free without subscription Best wishes Joe Neal and Pat PS This message is ONLY being sent to traders who have joined our email list or requested information from our web pages in the past We NEVER spam we hate SPAM Reply with a subject of REMOVE to be deleted from our email lists We do not make our members addresses available to anyone
